= popravi.mk

  * popravi.mk is a web application (built with Ruby on Rails) that allows people to help in detecting urban problems they have found on public area.
  * It includes a web service used by PopraviMK Android mobile application (built with Titanium Mobile and available on Android market)
  * PopraviMK mobile application is also winner of the first Android contest in Macedonia (2010) organized by Vip mobile operator: http://android.vip.mk/winners

== DEVELOPMENT NOTES

  * Application setup
    gem install bundler
    bundle install
    cp config/database.yml.template config/database.yml
    vim config/database.yml # edit database.yml file
    rake db:create
    rake db:migrate
    rake db:seed

  * Run cucumber features
    cucumber features

  * Run specs
    rspec spec

  * Fast reset
    rake db:drop && rake db:create && rake db:migrate && rake db:seed && rake db:test:prepare

